snippet.textDisplay:
Myself as a big music lover, I’ve been following and listening to Coke studio Pakistan 🇵🇰 ever since it started, always love it. And when our own coke studio 🇧🇩 launched its journey I became very glad, but at the same time, was doubtful about it whether it’s gonna up to the standard and do proper justice to our music or not. It did good so far, apart from few songs it actually produced some excellent music.
BUT Finally, after listening to this song, I now totally believe that we are also not running behind in terms of producing masterclass music like India or pakistan. This song is truly a masterpiece!!! Totally mind boggling!! Tremendous work on this one by team coke studio bangla👏👏👏! Keep going!
snippet.textOriginal:
